title: Miyavi - THIS IZ THE JAPANESE KABUKI ROCK [Ltd. Edition]
description:
This is the latest release by the popular Japanese rock artist, Miyavi.  This is the ltd. edition version, so there's a bonus DVD included which I've ripped and put on this torrent, which is why the torrent is so large.  If you don't want the DVD, you can simply deselect it while starting the download.  Please let me know if there are any problems.

Check out my journal entry on Last.fm--http://www.last.fm/user/GrannyGreen/journal/2008/01/20/7hc0b_my_cd_collection--for an up-to-date list on all the CDs that I own.  Feel free to ask for a rip of any one there...I'll rip it in any quality you want.
